PrecisAppointment of DOUGLAS G. RUCK, of Dartmouth, Nova Scotia, as a Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour on a full-time basis, for a term of four years; and order that DOUGLAS G. RUCK be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective June 25, 2001.
